sub_title: production of cosmetic products and biologically active additives
summary:
I have extensive experience in creating recipes for cosmetics and health supplements. I also have experience in the production of toothpaste with various abrasives. My pharmaceutical education allows me to use different components with the greatest efficiency, creating products that really work in the right direction. 
Now we are working with Ukrainian colleagues on a volunteer basis to make the hemostatic agent Plantor. My part of the work: searching for raw materials, creating regulatory and technical documentation, general technical and technological issues, working in a group to create presentations for investors.
